    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a significant overhaul, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and areas of surface rust. The interior has seen heavy use, with multiple tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is.",
