      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting flawless aesthetic integrity and mechanical perfection. Every detail, from the immaculate exterior finish to the preserved interior cabin, underscores a history of fastidious care. This is, without reservation, a peerless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
